WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:11.688
A new client brings documents, data, people and decisions that often remain in separate files.

2
00:00:11.688 --> 00:00:27.695
Vera carries them through one connected journey. It starts with the incoming folder, builds the inventory, gathers readable data and turns open points into precise requests.

3
00:00:27.695 --> 00:00:39.513
It then uses that same evidence to structure identity data, executors, beneficial owners, services and engagement terms.

4
00:00:39.513 --> 00:00:51.797
Engagement, privacy, AI information and the AML assessment share one basis. Actions, dates and reviews complete the file.

5
00:00:51.797 --> 00:01:02.685
The firm can see what is ready, what needs completing and which step comes next.

6
00:01:02.685 --> 00:01:09.200
From the first folder to an operational file that continues to follow the client.
